{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2106,"text":"To most of you, this is a device"},{"time":3984,"text":"to buy, sell, play games,"},{"time":6992,"text":"watch videos."},{"time":8902,"text":"I think it might be a lifeline."},{"time":11042,"text":"I think actually it might be able to save more lives"},{"time":13458,"text":"than penicillin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14958,"text":"Texting:"},{"time":16431,"text":"I know I say texting and a lot of you think sexting,"},{"time":19250,"text":"a lot of you think about the lewd photos that you see --"},{"time":22500,"text":"hopefully not your kids sending to somebody else --"},{"time":25125,"text":"or trying to translate the abbreviations"},{"time":26917,"text":"LOL, LMAO, HMU."},{"time":29875,"text":"I can help you with those later."},{"time":31708,"text":"But the parents in the room"},{"time":33750,"text":"know that texting is actually"},{"time":35375,"text":"the best way to communicate with your kids."},{"time":38000,"text":"It might be the only way to communicate with your kids."},{"time":40833,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":42500,"text":"The average teenager sends 3,339 text messages a month,"},{"time":47125,"text":"unless she's a girl, then it's closer to 4,000."},{"time":50625,"text":"And the secret is she opens every single one."},{"time":54208,"text":"Texting has a 100 percent open rate."},{"time":57917,"text":"Now the parents are really alarmed."},{"time":59333,"text":"It's a 100 percent open rate"},{"time":61167,"text":"even if she doesn't respond to you"},{"time":62917,"text":"when you ask her when she's coming home for dinner."},{"time":64667,"text":"I promise she read that text."},{"time":66208,"text":"And this isn't some suburban iPhone-using teen phenomenon."},{"time":72292,"text":"Texting actually overindexes"},{"time":73667,"text":"for minority and urban youth."},{"time":75750,"text":"I know this because at DoSomething.org,"},{"time":78625,"text":"which is the largest organization"},{"time":80333,"text":"for teenagers and social change in America,"},{"time":83292,"text":"about six months ago we pivoted"},{"time":84750,"text":"and started focusing on text messaging."},{"time":86375,"text":"We're now texting out to about 200,000 kids a week"},{"time":90583,"text":"about doing our campaigns to make their schools more green"},{"time":93292,"text":"or to work on homeless issues and things like that."},{"time":96458,"text":"We're finding it 11 times more powerful than email."},{"time":99875,"text":"We've also found an unintended consequence."},{"time":105958,"text":"We've been getting text messages back like these."},{"time":109000,"text":"\"I don't want to go to school today."},{"time":112250,"text":"The boys call me faggot.\""},{"time":114125,"text":"\"I was cutting, my parents found out,"},{"time":118708,"text":"and so I stopped."},{"time":120583,"text":"But I just started again an hour ago.\""},{"time":122792,"text":"Or, \"He won't stop raping me."},{"time":126083,"text":"He told me not to tell anyone."},{"time":127458,"text":"It's my dad. Are you there?\""},{"time":130250,"text":"That last one's an actual text message that we received."},{"time":133375,"text":"And yeah, we're there."},{"time":136125,"text":"I will not forget the day we got that text message."},{"time":138667,"text":"And so it was that day that we decided"},{"time":141083,"text":"we needed to build a crisis text hotline."},{"time":144208,"text":"Because this isn't what we do."},{"time":145708,"text":"We do social change."},{"time":147042,"text":"Kids are just sending us these text messages"},{"time":149042,"text":"because texting is so familiar and comfortable to them"},{"time":151958,"text":"and there's nowhere else to turn"},{"time":153750,"text":"that they're sending them to us."},{"time":156333,"text":"So think about it, a text hotline; it's pretty powerful."},{"time":158625,"text":"It's fast, it's pretty private."},{"time":160333,"text":"No one hears you in a stall, you're just texting quietly."},{"time":163750,"text":"It's real time."},{"time":165792,"text":"We can help millions of teens with counseling and referrals."},{"time":168954,"text":"That's great."},{"time":171208,"text":"But the thing that really makes this awesome is the data."},{"time":175625,"text":"Because I'm not really comfortable just helping that girl"},{"time":178125,"text":"with counseling and referrals."},{"time":179875,"text":"I want to prevent this shit from happening."},{"time":183375,"text":"So think about a cop."},{"time":186708,"text":"There's something in New York City."},{"time":188458,"text":"The police did it. It used to be just guess work, police work."},{"time":191000,"text":"And then they started crime mapping."},{"time":194583,"text":"And so they started following and watching"},{"time":195958,"text":"petty thefts, summonses, all kinds of things --"},{"time":199000,"text":"charting the future essentially."},{"time":200750,"text":"And they found things like,"},{"time":203458,"text":"when you see crystal meth on the street,"},{"time":205083,"text":"if you add police presence,"},{"time":206708,"text":"you can curb the otherwise inevitable spate"},{"time":209833,"text":"of assaults and robberies that would happen."},{"time":213417,"text":"In fact, the year after"},{"time":214542,"text":"the NYPD put CompStat in place,"},{"time":217167,"text":"the murder rate fell 60 percent."},{"time":220333,"text":"So think about the data from a crisis text line."},{"time":224875,"text":"There is no census on bullying and dating abuse"},{"time":228250,"text":"and eating disorders and cutting and rape --"},{"time":231167,"text":"no census."},{"time":232917,"text":"Maybe there's some studies, some longitudinal studies,"},{"time":235250,"text":"that cost lots of money and took lots of time."},{"time":237875,"text":"Or maybe there's some anecdotal evidence."},{"time":240250,"text":"Imagine having real time data"},{"time":243250,"text":"on every one of those issues."},{"time":244917,"text":"You could inform legislation."},{"time":246708,"text":"You could inform school policy."},{"time":248500,"text":"You could say to a principal,"},{"time":250583,"text":"\"You're having a problem every Thursday at three o'clock."},{"time":253375,"text":"What's going on in your school?\""},{"time":255333,"text":"You could see the immediate impact of legislation"},{"time":257875,"text":"or a hateful speech that somebody gives in a school assembly"},{"time":260167,"text":"and see what happens as a result."},{"time":263708,"text":"This is really, to me,"},{"time":265375,"text":"the power of texting and the power of data."},{"time":268750,"text":"Because while people are talking about data,"},{"time":271000,"text":"making it possible for Facebook"},{"time":272583,"text":"to mine my friend from the third grade,"},{"time":274833,"text":"or Target to know when it's time for me to buy more diapers,"},{"time":277792,"text":"or some dude to build a better baseball team,"},{"time":280792,"text":"I'm actually really excited about the power of data and the power of texting"},{"time":285958,"text":"to help that kid go to school,"},{"time":288083,"text":"to help that girl stop cutting in the bathroom"},{"time":290167,"text":"and absolutely to help that girl whose father's raping her."},{"time":294083,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":296875,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}